Create a beginner-friendly full-stack Node.js project called "utsav-registration-portal" for college students.

Tech stack:
- Node.js
- Express.js
- SQLite using sqlite3 package
- HTML, CSS, vanilla JavaScript
- Express session for login handling

Goal:
Build a college utsav registration portal where students can register, log in, view events, join events, and where an admin can view all events and participants.

Functional requirements:

1. User registration
- A new user can register with:
  - full name
  - email
  - password
  - college name
- Email should be unique
- Store users in SQLite database

2. User login
- User can log in using email and password
- Maintain session after login
- Show different UI for admin and normal user

